(61, 61, 'Kevin 英文不難', 'https://files.soundon.fm/1600479883555-b45956e1-8edb-4bec-84f0-9d06a2dfce56.jpeg', '我用輕鬆聊天的方式訓練你的英文聽力和單字量，每週三、五早上更新。合作邀約：english.great.easy@gmail.com\n\n--\nHosting provided by SoundOn', 'Education', 'english.great.easy@gmail.com', '我用輕鬆聊天的方式訓練你的英文聽力和單字量，每週三、五早上更新。合作邀約：english.great.easy@gmail.com', '用輕鬆聊天的方式訓練你的英文聽力和增加單字量', 'https://api.soundon.fm/v2/podcasts/5c3172bb-4d57-43c4-8793-1513f8aebb99/feed.xml', '2.4', 0, '0', 0, '2020-10-23'),
(62, 62, '听故事学中文 Learning Chinese through Stories', 'https://ssl-static.libsyn.com/p/assets/f/d/1/0/fd1070f71b09336a/Webp.net-resizeimage_1.png', 'Using more than 99% target language, 听故事学中文Learning Chinese through Stories(LCTS) creates authentic and immersive podcasts to help people around the world develop Chinese language skills and cultural competency. It covers a wide range of topics and proficiency levels(Novice, Intermediate, Advanced). Every story has two parts: story (A)  and story explanation (B), accompanied by annotated vocabulary and transcript.  For example, an episode titled \"2.3.12 A\" means this episode is at the level of Intermediate High (2.3), is the 12th episode created for this level, and is the story, not story explanation. You can also read along with the stories and explanations by becoming our patrons. \r\nhttps://www.patreon.com/learningchinesethroughstories', 'Education', 'support@learningchinesethroughstories.com', 'Using more than 99% target language, 听故事学中文Learning Chinese through Stories(LCTS) creates authentic and immersive podcasts to help people around the world develop Chinese language skills and cultural competency. It covers a wide range of topics and proficiency levels(Novice, Intermediate, Advanced). Every story has two parts: story (A)  and story explanation (B), accompanied by annotated vocabulary and transcript.  For example, an episode titled \"2.3.12 A\" means this episode is at the level of Intermediate High (2.3), is the 12th episode created for this level, and is the story, not story explanation. You can also read along with the stories and explanations by becoming our patrons. \r\nhttps://www.patreon.com/learningchinesethroughstories', 'Chinese Podcast, Chinese Immersion, Learning Mandarin, Learning Chinese, Advanced Chinese, Learn Mandarin Chinese, Chinese Stories, Authentic Chinese, Chinese Listening, Chinese TPRS, Chinese Slangs, Idioms, Native Chinese Speakers', 'https://learningchinesethroughstories.libsyn.com/rss', '3.5', 0, '0', 0, '2020-10-23'),
(63, 63, '佐編茶水間', 'https://zoeyk.co/wp-content/uploads/powerpress/podcast-623.jpg', '佐編茶水間是一個討論「遠距工作、自我成長、品牌經營」的Podcast節目，教導你如何打造一個不被地點限制的事業，創造能夠一邊工作、一邊旅行的理想生活。  在這裡，我們會討論如何解決職場、生活上的生理與心理面困擾，也會邀請同樣在人生道路上，追求理想生活的職人分享他們的故事，並帶給也想要追求夢想的你，更多靈感與動力。', 'Education', 'podcast@zoeyk.co', '佐編茶水間是一個討論「遠距工作、自我成長、品牌經營」的Podcast節目，教導你如何打造一個不被地點限制的事業，創造能夠一邊工作、一邊旅行的理想生活。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n在這裡，我們會討論如何解決職場、生活上的生理與心理面困擾，也會邀請同樣在人生道路上，追求理想生活的職人分享他們的故事，並帶給也想要追求夢想的你，更多靈感與動力。', '佐編茶水間', 'https://zoeyk.co/feed/podcast/', '2.8', 0, '0', 0, '2020-10-23'),
