(59, ' 無線耳塞式耳機', '搭載凝聚高性能精簡設計的Ø9.8mm驅動單元，展現優質的中高音頻,重視佩戴舒適感的袖珍機身，耳型較小也能完美服貼,電池盒Clip-On固定夾，可將耳機穩定固定於後領，提升使用便利性,多功能控制器，可於耳邊操作音樂、影片播放及通話,對應音質表現佳的AAC編碼,跟各種造型完美搭配的6種繽紛色彩', 2400, 'https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-01_kfxl-b5.png', 'https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-02.png,https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-03.png,https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-04.png,https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-05.png,https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-06.png,https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-07.png,https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-08.png,https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-09.png,https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-10.png,https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-11.png,https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-12.png,https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-13.png,https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-14.png,https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-15.png,https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-16.png,https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-17.png,https://www.audio-technica.com.tw/images/thumbnails/500/500/detailed/7/ATH-CKR35BT-18.png', '[\"通訊方式\",\"通訊使用頻段\",\"通訊距離\",\"調變方式\",\"支援Bluetooth協定\",\"支援編碼\",\"傳輸頻率範圍\",\"NCC 型式認證號碼\",\"型號\",\"型式\",\"驅動單元\",\"輸出感度\",\"頻率響應\",\"輸入阻抗\",\"電源型式\",\"充電時間\",\"電池續航力\",\"待機時間\",\"工作溫度範圍\",\"通